{"TopicId":160531,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Dril-o-matic as landing struts?","CreatedByName":"juvilado","CreatedById":106978,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-12T08:19:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"juvilado","CreatedById":106978,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-12T08:19:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi, has anyone tried using Drill-o-matics as landing struts? Do they work?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i68.tinypic.com/t6s4uf.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022t6s4uf.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-12T08:35:17Z\u0022 title=\u002205/12/2017 08:35  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 12, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by juvilado\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DrLicor","CreatedById":165712,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-12T09:33:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe drills go into the ground don\u0027t they?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, what are the advantages of these over normal landing struts? Landingstruts are much cheaper and most important; lighter. Which saves you a plenty amount of delta-v.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"juvilado","CreatedById":106978,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-12T10:01:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223054197\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494581631\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165712\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DrLicor\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n25 minutes ago, DrLicor said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe drills go into the ground don\u0027t they?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, what are the advantages of these over normal landing struts? Landingstruts are much cheaper and most important; lighter. Which saves you a plenty amount of delta-v.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell i can think about these advantages:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1.- Faster mining\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2.- No need of landing struts\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut yes, they go into the ground and didn\u0027t even noticed any succesful\u00A0balancing effect when touching land...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-12T18:54:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe \u0027drill head\u0027 and skinny part of the drill shaft have no colliders (meaning, as far as the game knows, they\u0027re not really there). \u00A0The lowest part of the moving collider is the widest part of the grey shaft. \u00A0Which means it\u0027s not much lower than the drill base itself. \u00A0It can be done - but not much advantage over landing gear or legs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-13T06:49:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223054213\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494583305\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106978\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022juvilado\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, juvilado said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1.- Faster mining\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t follow your reasoning on that one.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-13T09:00:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen you are mining, the drill heads move. If you are using them as landing legs at the time, your entire ship will bounce up and down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"juvilado","CreatedById":106978,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-13T11:17:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223055109\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494658157\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166502\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spricigo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Spricigo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t follow your reasoning on that one.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, i suppose 3 drills will mine faster than one...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-13T15:58:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223055224\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160531\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494674238\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106978\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022juvilado\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, juvilado said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, i suppose 3 drills will mine faster than one...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, \u00A0but using landing legs will not prevent you to use more drills.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}